me, two widely different thermal\ntransport regimes, i.e. ballistic systems, with no temperature gradient, and\ndiffusive systems with a temperature gradient.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Dec 2015 16:54:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2016 16:59:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 30 Apr 2016 14:44:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-11"}
