tripped\ndisk material includes dust grains ranging in size from small grains at the\nleading edge, typical of star forming regions, to large grains, ices or pebbles\nproducing grey or nearly grey extinction deeper within the occulting material.\nIt is not known whether this material represents arrested planet building prior\nto the tidal disruption event, or perhaps accelerated planet building as a\nresult of the disruption event, but in any case the evidence suggests the\npresence of advanced planet building material in the space between RW Aur A and\nB.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Dec 2015 17:55:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-03"}
