tice symmetry, magnetic ordering,\nferroelectricity generation, electromagnon excitations, multiferroic domain\nstructure and domain wall dynamics, and interfacial coupling in multiferroic\nheterostructures, will be revisited in an updated framework of physics. In\naddition, several emergent phenomena and related physics, including magnetic\nskyrmions and generic topological structures associated with magnetoelectricity\nwill be discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 12 Dec 2015 01:09:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 16 Jan 2016 09:46:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-19"}
